name: Elite

episodes.name: Welcome
episodes.overview: After a public high school collapses, the builder tries to repair its image by paying for three impacted students to attend an exclusive private school.

episodes.name: Desire
episodes.overview: A school project brings Marina and Samuel closer, and inspires Guzmán to try and win over Nadia. Meanwhile, Christian is shocked by a revelation.

episodes.name: Saturday Night
episodes.overview: Samuel throws a party, where Nano makes a move on Marina and spiked punch affects more than one couple. Nadia is hurt by what she learns about Guzmán.

episodes.name: Love Is a Drug
episodes.overview: Guzmán tries to earn Nadia's forgiveness. Polo and Christian bond at a gala. Lu bribes her teacher. To pay his debt, Nano must complete a dark mission.

episodes.name: Everyone Lies
episodes.overview: Marina gives Nano a way to pay his debt. Lu intentionally leaks a secret in front of Nadia. Omar learns Ander told his friends about the two of them.

episodes.name: Everything Will Be Okay
episodes.overview: Nano learns one watch holds a secret. Marina's pot stash is found. News of a pregnancy raises suspicions. Christian is offered fame if he does a favor.

episodes.name: Everything Explodes
episodes.overview: Carla suspects Marina is involved in the theft. Omar's father makes plans for his son. After learning his sister’s secret, Guzmán seeks revenge.

episodes.name: Assilah
episodes.overview: The last moments before the murder unfold. Christian makes a tough decision. The police arrest a suspect. Guzmán becomes reckless with grief.

1.name: Season 1
1.overview: When three working-class teens enroll in an exclusive private school in Spain, the clash between them and the wealthy students leads to murder.

episodes.name: 20 hours missing
episodes.overview: New students start school at Las Encinas as Guzmán continues to mourn his sister and Christian struggles with his secret. A classmate goes missing.

episodes.name: 34 hours missing
episodes.overview: Seeking the truth about Marina's death, Samuel attempts to seduce Carla. Lu's new friend, social media guru Cayetana, hosts an impromptu party.

episodes.name: 36 hours missing
episodes.overview: Polo and Ander have a heart-to-heart. Nadia gets creative to stop Guzmán from drinking too much and doing drugs. Rebeka's mother offers Samuel a job.

episodes.name: 59 hours missing
episodes.overview: Pressured by his friends, Polo's guilt overwhelms him. Cayetana's mother threatens to reveal her secret. Ander and Guzmán argue with their partners.

episodes.name: 63 hours missing
episodes.overview: Rebeka teases Cayetana with what she's learned. The Halloween party takes a troubling turn. Samuel walks in on a shocking scene.

episodes.name: 66 hours missing
episodes.overview: Lu blackmails Nadia, and Samuel confronts Carla with his suspicions. In the future, Guzmán is interrogated about the missing student.

episodes.name: 84 hours missing
episodes.overview: Lu uncovers a secret while helping Cayetana with her fundraiser party. Omar worries about Samuel's fate. Ander's behavior confuses Guzmán.

episodes.name: 0 hours missing
episodes.overview: Painful truths and dark secrets are exposed as the students unburden themselves and the circumstances behind Samuel's disappearance are revealed.

2.name: Season 2
2.overview: In the wake of a classmate's death, a student vanishes, allegiances shift, new friends join the drama, and dark secrets become too difficult to contain.

episodes.name: Carla
episodes.overview: Carla is interrogated when a student is killed at a party. In the past, she faces Polo in court, Ander has a health worry, and Nadia meets a new suitor.

episodes.name: Samuel and Guzmán
episodes.overview: Guzmán attempts to make amends. Nadia threatens payback when she and Lu go after the same scholarship. Ander comes clean to his loved ones.

episodes.name: Cayetana and Valerio
episodes.overview: Polo is harassed at school. Samuel mulls the police's offer as he and Rebeca become closer. Ander struggles with his treatment.

episodes.name: Lu
episodes.overview: Guzmán confronts Nadia's father. New romances transpire when Lu throws a creative Valentine's Day party. Rebeka struggles with a moneymaking decision.

episodes.name: Ander
episodes.overview: Rebeka tries to identify the traitor. A blackout party at the club leads to multiple shocking revelations.

episodes.name: Rebeka
episodes.overview: The Columbia scholarship winner is announced. Nadia makes a momentous decision. Samuel's concern about Carla causes issues between him and Valerio.

episodes.name: Nadia and Omar
episodes.overview: As graduation day arrives, the futures of multiple students remain uncertain. Polo begs his mothers to reconsider their recent decision.

episodes.name: Polo
episodes.overview: The events that transpired the night of the murder unfold. The police interview several eyewitnesses who are ready to point fingers.

3.name: Season 3
3.overview: When another classmate is killed, a new investigation ensues. The students look toward their future, while the consequences of the past haunt them.

episodes.name: The New Order
episodes.overview: A stern principal and three new students begin at Las Encinas. Omar and Samuel must prove themselves academically while their friends try to help.

episodes.name: Five Seconds
episodes.overview: Prince Phillipe's arrival at the school prompts strict security measures and controversy. Samuel and Omar's towel party leads to new romantic hookups.

episodes.name: When Lies Dance with Temptation
episodes.overview: When Prince Phillippe hosts his famous Le Bal party, betrayals ensue. The jealousy between Guzmán and Samuel intensifies. Patrick sparks friction.

episodes.name: I'm a...
episodes.overview: Rebe is confused and hurt by Mencía's mysterious behavior. Much to Ari's chagrin, Benjamín suggests Samuel join the debate team.

episodes.name: Reintegration
episodes.overview: Ari and Samuel face off in an important and public debate. After speaking with Ander, Omar struggles with the emotional fallout.

episodes.name: I Love You All Wrong
episodes.overview: Phillippe worries that his friends are using him for Ambar Lucid performance tickets. Rebe warns Mencía she feels skeptical about Armando's assistance.

episodes.name: Before I Go (1)
episodes.overview: Samuel tells Ari to make her choice while Guzmán plans a romantic date. Cayetana is stunned by a realization. Mencía is backed into a corner.

episodes.name: Before I Go (2)
episodes.overview: The details of Ari's attack are revealed but the Las Encinas students prove yet again there is always more than meets the eye.

4.name: Season 4
4.overview: A strict principal and four new students arrive at Las Encinas, bringing an onslaught of romantic entanglements, intense rumors and a fresh mystery.

episodes.name: I Killed Him
episodes.overview: A new student catches Patrick's eye while another surprises Cayetana by defending Phillipe. Benjamín implements stricter measures at school.

episodes.name: Anything Goes
episodes.overview: Patrick lashes out at his dad by hosting a hedonistic party for everyone at the school. Samuel struggles with keeping both Ari and Benjamín happy.

episodes.name: Tie Me Up
episodes.overview: Tensions grow between Omar and Samuel as the students vote for someone to be expelled. Isadora tries to persuade Phillipe that she knows what's best.

episodes.name: The Body
episodes.overview: While helping her father with an auction, Mencía makes a shocking discovery. Outside of the event, Omar is surprised by what he finds in the water.

episodes.name: Please, Tell the Truth
episodes.overview: The police investigation forces Benjamín into the spotlight. Patrick finds himself in a tough spot with Iván and Cruz. Caye reconnects with a friend.

episodes.name: Can't Buy My Love
episodes.overview: The students auction off dates to raise money for Samuel's bail, but the results of the bidding cause more than one broken heart.

episodes.name: Toxic
episodes.overview: Samuel, Rebe and Cayetana look for evidence that could implicate Benjamín. Heartbroken over Phillipe's harsh words, Isadora embarks on a trip to Ibiza.

episodes.name: Your Side of the World and Mine
episodes.overview: Samu considers his next move with the SIM card, Cruz gives Iván relationship advice, and Caye tries to support a traumatized Isadora.

5.name: Season 5
5.overview: At Las Encinas, the new semester means new love triangles, new students, new rules — and a new mysterious crime.

episodes.name: Anxiety
episodes.overview: Ari, Mencía and Patrick return to school, determined not to let their family's baggage weigh them down. Isa's new club opens with a big first night.

episodes.name: Selfies
episodes.overview: After a new development in Isa's case against her rapists, everyone has an opinion. Ari asks Nico out for a drink. Patrick makes a sacrifice.

episodes.name: Naked
episodes.overview: Isa's friends rally round — and strip down — to support her. Rocío practices a new talent. Mencía starts to wonder about Sara and Raúl's relationship.

episodes.name: War
episodes.overview: The crew turns out for Cruz's championship football match, where controversy leads to chaos — and then shocking violence. Sara makes a painful decision.

episodes.name: Mourning
episodes.overview: Javi plants an idea in Isa's head that she can't shake, while Patrick struggles to help Iván process a loss. Raúl isn't ready to let go of Saraul.Goals.

episodes.name: Tina
episodes.overview: Iván seeks emotional release, Sara slips back into old routines, and Ari goes looking for closure. When Isa proposes a collaboration, Nico has doubts.

episodes.name: Masks
episodes.overview: A Venetian Carnival night at Isadora House shows Isa a new side of Dídac and puts the students of Las Encinas on a collision course toward heartbreak.

episodes.name: Separation
episodes.overview: Still reeling from the night before, Ari takes on the heavy responsibility of protecting her siblings. Hugo's past actions finally catch up with him.

6.name: Season 6
6.overview: Everybody's looking for something this year at Las Encinas, whether it's love, revenge or millions of followers. But will they all make it out alive?

episodes.name: Las Encinas
episodes.overview: An old student is tempted to return to Las Encinas as Isadora struggles with her feelings for Dídac. Iván feels lonely — but that might change soon.

episodes.name: Protocol
episodes.overview: Chloe and Carmen are both obsessed with Iván — but for different reasons. Coach Jessica advises Sara. The mysterious academic director focuses on Dídac.

episodes.name: Bling-Bling
episodes.overview: Sara throws a steamy glitter party. Family tensions tear Dídac and Isadora apart. Rocío and Eric’s night in the squatters’ house spirals out of control.

episodes.name: Semicolon
episodes.overview: Chloe considers opening up to Eric, while Nico is worried about his cousin's behavior. Omar deals with the consequences of his past in Las Encinas.

episodes.name: The Family
episodes.overview: Sara gets Chloe's help while scheming against Raúl. Omar catches Joel and Iván in an awkward situation. Carmen makes a bold move.

episodes.name: At Rock Bottom
episodes.overview: Isadora makes tough decisions in the family business. Luis' investigation is threatened. Deception leaves Chloe in a vulnerable place.

episodes.name: Just Hug Me
episodes.overview: Raúl manipulates Sara's revenge to his advantage. Iván’s presence puts Omar and Joel’s relationship in a very confusing place.

episodes.name: I'm Gonna End This Forever
episodes.overview: A new death shocks the students of Las Encinas. Iván makes a last-minute proposal to Joel, while Isadora must decide what to do with her parents.

7.name: Season 7
7.overview: Omar is back. Iván has a broken heart. Isadora deals with her dangerous family. Is it possible for the students at Las Encinas to trust one another?

episodes.name: Alumni
episodes.overview: Nadia's return surprises Omar. Isadora and Chloe compete for entry into the exclusive and mysterious Alumni, where Joel captures Héctor's attention.

episodes.name: To the Edge
episodes.overview: The rift between Joel and Iván widens as Héctor comes between them. Chloe makes a heartbreaking choice, and Carmen receives a startling message.

episodes.name: Combustion
episodes.overview: A dangerous event raises the stakes for Joel and Isadora, who can't afford to lose the grand prize. Dalmar's scheme further puts him in hot water.

episodes.name: I Belong to No One
episodes.overview: A fiery encounter offers Joel a lucrative new avenue. Chloe lays out a trap. A new foe puts Omar's life on the line. Sara and Nico get closer.

episodes.name: The Last Night
episodes.overview: Desperate, Dalmar considers a new strategy as Chloe and Eric devise theirs. Joel share his secret with Iván. Luis' obsession with Isadora grows.

episodes.name: Guilty
episodes.overview: A shocking murder leads to two arrests. Emilia and Héctor make a plan as Omar conducts his own investigation. Sara learns more about Raúl's death.

episodes.name: Like Siblings
episodes.overview: Héctor and Emilia's bond splits. Nadia urges Omar to report his attackers. As the murder probe proceeds, Iván, Isadora and Sara suspect Chloe and Eric.

episodes.name: End of Term
episodes.overview: Isadora takes justice into her own hands. Chloe and Carmen make their final play. When an incriminating video circulates, Las Encinas takes a last hit.
